      "content": "i know they love me, but it feels selfish to keep letting them do everything for me. it's just constant. every time they have to help me move or cook, i can see them getting tired. i feel like a broken thing they're just trying to fix, but i can't be fixed. it would be so much easier for everyone if i just wasn't a problem to deal with anymore.",
